    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. This car is in breathtaking condition\u2014it looks and feels like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered it since day one. There isn't a single blemish to be found, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and maintained to absolute perfection, you've found it. Come check it out\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
