    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's spotless inside and out, runs like a total dream, and you can really tell it\u2019s been loved. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Come take a look, you're going to fall in love with it! \u2728",
