    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated S54 inline-six era. The power plant is in peak mechanical health, featuring a meticulously maintained Double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies that provide instantaneous throttle response across the power band. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with documented subframe reinforcement, while the suspension geometry retains its factory precision. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example with zero deferred maintenance on the rod bearings or cooling system, offering a pure, high-revving analog experience.",
